The United States welcomes the formation of a new cabinet in Yemen and commends the efforts of President Hadi, Prime Minister Bahah, and the country's political leadership in creating an inclusive government. The US is committed to supporting Yemenis as they work towards implementing peace agreements and political reforms. The cabinet should represent unity and prioritize the goals of the nation over individual or partisan interests. The US also reaffirms its partnership with Yemen in promoting political and economic reform and countering the threat from al-Qa'ida in the Arabian Peninsula.